NOVATEK MICROELE August Sales Fall 5.67% (Table) : 3034 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-09-06T06:39:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-06/novatek-microele-august-sales-fall-5-67-table-3034-tt.html
NOVATEK MICROELE said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 5.67% to NT$3,031,032,000 from NT$3,213,185,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales           3,031,032        3,213,185   
YOY%              -5.67%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           23,757,163       24,451,984  
YOY%              -2.84% 
=================================================================
 